WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:02.169
Previously on "Ghost Whisperer..."

00:02.339 --> 00:04.303
No! Wake up, mommy, wake up!

00:04.304 --> 00:06.064
Melinda! Oh, my God.

00:06.400 --> 00:09.051
It was a vision, you're OK!

00:09.086 --> 00:10.563
It felt so real.

00:10.597 --> 00:12.804
Honey, they're just
getting worse and worse.

00:12.839 --> 00:15.480
Melinda said Carl was afraid the
shadows were getting in his head.

00:15.515 --> 00:18.759
You think the shadows are
messing with Melinda's head?

00:18.793 --> 00:20.234
We protect each other.

00:20.268 --> 00:22.271
Whenever the cold things come.

00:22.306 --> 00:24.212
The shadows.

00:24.246 --> 00:25.316
Your son is in danger.

00:25.350 --> 00:27.853
So what you're saying
is that I can fix this

00:27.888 --> 00:30.925
If I make Aiden not see
ghosts. Or shadows.

00:30.960 --> 00:32.029
Don't you think we owe
it to Aiden to try?

00:32.063 --> 00:33.531
By changing him?

00:33.566 --> 00:36.520
If it would keep my son safe
and alive, I don't care.

